The love and genuine better days that have come into our lives
Soon nothing will matter
its not something immaturly said
theres something felt and its good
not a fairy tale love
just tell me why the people are dumb
No matter what road you take
theyll always find a way to hate you
things to make fun of you for
well im proud that this is my social flaw
the best things in my life
are not up to the cool kids standards
the music and the love and the friends and the experiences and the laughter in my life
is what makes it better than all the antiband-dishonest-jealous people



My life grows only stronger
imperfect days are still that much better than thier best

So supposedly all of the other kids in chorus concider me and everyone else on stage the " stage people".....  that is kinda weird.  and its weirder that i never knew.

college?  less than 3 years?  It used to be easy.  I was set for Julliard.   But then I found out about so many other colleges,  and so many people I know didnt make Julliard.  But Mr Richards said I could do it.  < look at this faith>   College...  what a ways away,  it will be like.. tomorrrow
